data.description: Magnificent ranch-style home on a cul-de-sac in Brentwood Village! Be the new proud owner of this nearly 3,000 sq ft  5 bed, 3 bath, 2-car garage home that has been carefully maintained and move-in ready! This home is perfect for families with young kids as you live on a quiet street with a large front yard and elegant, landscaped setback. The elevated covered front stoop opens to a tiled entryway leading to an open floor plan-style space. Enjoy having a formal living room with a fireplace, formal dining room, a casual breakfast nook by a peninsula kitchen, and dramatic railing overlooking the floor-to-ceiling windows affording you with views to the spacious private backyard! The master suite on the main floor has its own private deck and a bath with his and hers sinks and a corner garden tub. Two large bedrooms have hall bath access to a second full bath with tub. Need more space? The finished lower level offers you two more bedrooms, a third full bath, entertainment area, and a wet bar you could convert into a full kitchen if you wish. Or bring your entertaining outdoors in the spacious open deck looking out to the fully fenced private backyard. The lot is spacious at 0.28 acres with plenty of mature trees, allotted space for a playset, and even a small pond.  Aside from the stellar layout, enjoy the finer things life has to offer with a home that has exquisite finishes, skylights, hardwood floors on the main level, tile flooring downstairs, and recent roof and appliance updates! Live in an easily accessible part of SE Wichita close to the shopping and dining district, McConnell AFB, and other relevant spots in the city. If you are in the market for a dream home then make sure to check out this one! Schedule an exclusive showing appointment by picking up your phone and calling us today!
